{"tid":423816,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<係真唔係？未經證實>BNO申請唔到多次入台證 ？因為平權在即？","createTime":"2017-10-04T08:21:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T10:06:53.000Z","uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"eff3247ba09fc19f7a78e21bd7d1f4ba0147685f","tid":423816,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T08:21:04.000Z","msg":"BNO申請唔到 多次入台證 ？因為平權在即？<br />\n<br />\n2017-10-03&nbsp;/ by&nbsp;martinoei 黃世澤<br />\n<br />\n台灣政府推出網上申請 多次入台證 服務，方便需要經常出入台灣嘅香港人，只不過，呢次出現一個好特別嘅條款，就係你持有 BNO 係唔可以申請 多次入台證 ，點解會出現咁奇怪嘅政策。如果台灣將會修改《港澳關係條例》或者BNO將會平權，咁呢個政策會係好正常。<br />\n<br />\nBNO平權後唔駛 多次入台證<br />\n過往BNO入境台灣要入台證，因為中華民國政府唔承認英國佔領香港，所以作出嘅奇怪安排。如果你持英國公民護照，就可以免簽直接喺台灣逗留。只不過，唔少BN(HK)A 1997嘅人，會用BNO入境台灣，除咗因為BNO保證回港外，另一方面，係節省英國護照上嘅空間用，可以節省申請護照嘅錢，呢招怪招我識有部分印度同巴基斯坦裔同時有BC同BNO嘅人用，雖然呢班友技術上並唔係中華民國國民嚟。<br />\n<br />\n但如果台灣政府會改變對BNO嘅取態，就另一回事，其實台灣政府用英國BNO護照呢個字，都反映咗呢個取態，事實上，英國駐台灣辦公室，可以對BNO提供領事保護，BNO變相喺台灣視為英國人，如果台灣政府決定俾BNO直接免入台證入境，咁俾申請多次入台證入境係完全無意思，而且可能會喺短期內改變政策。承認BNO持有人係英國人，呢個喺台灣政策上醞釀咗一段時間，亦有唔少香港人向台北方面爭取，呢個係其中一個可能性。<br />\n<br />\n但另一個可能性，係BNO平權在即，如果英國打算為BNO平權，台灣政府獲知會嘅話，咁就無必要俾BNO申請 多次入台證 ，因為如果英國要平權BNO，喺國會立法前嘅預備工作係十分之重大，特別係預先通知部分經常接待BNO嘅國家喺技術上作出安排，而台灣肯定係其中一個。你估彭定康會無喇喇討香港人歡心話會向國會提出BNO平權？要進行平權，係好多技術上安排要處理，特別依家涉及BREXIT，技術上有好多複雜嘢。而台灣內政部應該收到英國嘅知會，知道大概嘅平權時間，因此作出安排，因為BNO一旦平權，港澳關係條例亦唔會適用，理論上，一旦BNO平咗權，就會變晒BC，屆時喺中華民國法律技術上，佢地係華僑，梗係不適用港澳關係條例。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://martinoei.com/article/16023/bno%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E5%94%94%E5%88%B0-%E5%A4%9A%E6%AC%A1%E5%85%A5%E5%8F%B0%E8%AD%89-%EF%BC%9F%E5%9B%A0%E7%82%BA%E5%B9%B3%E6%AC%8A%E5%9C%A8%E5%8D%B3%EF%BC%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmartinoei.com%2Farticle%2F16023%2Fbno%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%2588%25B0-%25E5%25A4%259A%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%258F%25B0%25E8%25AD%2589-%25EF%25BC%259F%25E5%259B%25A0%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%259C%25A8%25E5%258D%25B3%25EF%25BC%259F&d=lTlDmaOwc5TUNbs8m0aHRPjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=110ce2bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://martinoei.com/article/16023/bno%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E5%94%94%E5%88%B0-%E5%A4%9A%E6%AC%A1%E5%85%A5%E5%8F%B0%E8%AD%89-%EF%BC%9F%E5%9B%A0%E7%82%BA%E5%B9%B3%E6%AC%8A%E5%9C%A8%E5%8D%B3%EF%BC%9F</a>"},{"pid":"37b0bb5dfdb01f29d02fa335d623bdc64fb75aae","tid":423816,"uid":55732,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T08:44:18.000Z","msg":"越嚟越頂唔撚順呢條友<br />\n<br />\nBNO平權當然係一件好事<br />\n<br />\n但條友就嚟ff到英國佬去中環街市痾篤屎都講到BNO平權真係好撚難頂，今時今日啲時事評論員係咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到咁呀？"},{"pid":"105c973e460f9bd73a8b96a201f8b5e374245a13","tid":423816,"uid":63669,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T08:47:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uhd4r6lq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuhd4r6lq&h=9f3e4deb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0453551b9a5159de49e5b187864dec5e0d04285","tid":423816,"uid":21873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T08:49:16.000Z","msg":"好事黎<br />\n不過依d遲d先知都得<br />\n整係想知幾時平"},{"pid":"e46bd8fd610164d2bd8d957e0ed009de28e590d0","tid":423816,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T09:05:18.000Z","msg":"搵唔到佢講話bno唔可以申請source"},{"pid":"72329f584d5c81989f3e0728770dd37d938e1ff6","tid":423816,"uid":106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T09:08:47.000Z","msg":"就黎支國唔認 BNO 都係平權在即<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11bbd741ddf55ebf7e0018061630f8ac24570577","tid":423816,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T09:09:19.000Z","msg":"世柒就算數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6614f8b266e6454be4ca833e02218c6bcaaab00","tid":423816,"uid":64073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T09:10:38.000Z","msg":"又係呢條友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  真係平咗嘅事後會比返個like佢嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77d6b8d9aeec2cb9d8e2e61aa173cfd55d0aff8b","tid":423816,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T09:17:01.000Z","msg":"我要申請 - <br />\n香港澳門居民短期停留申請人必須符合下列資格之一：<br />\n有香港永久居留資格，且未持有英國BNO或香港以外護照。<br />\n<br />\n有澳門永久居留資格，且未持有澳門護照以外之旅行證照或雖持有葡萄牙護照，但係於葡萄牙結束治理前於澳門取得。<br />\n<a href=\"https://coa.immigration.gov.tw/coa-frontend/overseas-honk-macao\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcoa.immigration.gov.tw%2Fcoa-frontend%2Foverseas-honk-macao&d=lTlDmaOwc5TUNbs8m0aHRPjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=5aa51aa1\" target=\"_blank\">https://coa.immigration.gov.tw/coa-frontend/overseas-honk-macao</a><br />\n世柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4ccadd56a4da843a97fb7eec6a4ea7d8fb14a99","tid":423816,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T09:25:10.000Z","msg":"中肯講句，技術上係會有知會其他國家先既<br />\n雖然我都覺佢好煩，好多猜測<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f29fbb25f7e91a7dccb64826c39d06211681d2a","tid":423816,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T10:09:21.000Z","msg":"你話bno當英國護照咪夠， 平權就拉埋黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"582f6990359b87ad543753a0eaee7ad76f9a21f4","tid":423816,"uid":59690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T10:28:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/uhd4r6lq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuhd4r6lq&h=9f3e4deb&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb85b2370f7b12d2b612ddd0cc0c2543299a604","tid":423816,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T10:33:40.000Z","msg":"根本亂up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢個申請界面係可以用BNO。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/230530_7a720ebcc003dd784abe2dc70bdd5676.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F230530_7a720ebcc003dd784abe2dc70bdd5676.JPG&h=17fd5174&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4496613f8e30c884445b507436eb0e82d999dcc","tid":423816,"uid":42250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T10:06:53.000Z","msg":"好撚柒啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}